    "description": "1970年的瑞典，冷战打响。尘封已久的成千上万座防空洞，如今总算要派上用场。防空警报响起时，你和另外24名玩家将在不同公寓中开始游戏。时间不多，所以无论身在何方、无论用什么手段，都一定要尽可能收集物资和武器。<br><br>可以找到什么装备？能够制作何等物资？什么人值得信任？利用 Shattle 游戏内语音聊天功能，你既可结识朋友，也可制造敌人。要想在三波炸弹袭击下幸免于难、成功抵达安全之地，就要将每一个脑细胞都动用起来。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>20分钟一回合</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730580/extras/dc0b01d996fe5bc49aa62b0f652f94cd.poster.avif?t=1693311930\" width=612 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730580/extras/dc0b01d996fe5bc49aa62b0f652f94cd.webm?t=1693311930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730580/extras/dc0b01d996fe5bc49aa62b0f652f94cd.mp4?t=1693311930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>不用东躲西藏，别再守株待兔——你没那个美国时间。即便不择手段，也要活到最后。你必须深谋远虑，但记得动作一定要快。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>近战生存游戏</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730580/extras/b143a6a14bbd991447d57962ed4356c5.poster.avif?t=1693311930\" width=614 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730580/extras/b143a6a14bbd991447d57962ed4356c5.webm?t=1693311930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730580/extras/b143a6a14bbd991447d57962ed4356c5.mp4?t=1693311930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>从茂密森林和地堡，到防空洞和地下隧道，你难免要与其他玩家狭路相逢，这时候就要打出一条生路。小心！转角遇到的未必是爱，还可能是血光之灾。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>可破坏场景</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730580/extras/39c568a213d1fb619afc6ad7cfcccf9e.poster.avif?t=1693311930\" width=614 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730580/extras/39c568a213d1fb619afc6ad7cfcccf9e.webm?t=1693311930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730580/extras/39c568a213d1fb619afc6ad7cfcccf9e.mp4?t=1693311930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>炸弹从天而降时，也会裹挟大块游戏场景落下，从而在森林地区和建筑群处打造更多充满变数的全新空间。所以，每次离开防空洞，都做好迎接全新环境的准备吧。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丰富的武器与护甲</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730580/extras/ac1140800ca7c74fbd09a0dba1717bdd.poster.avif?t=1693311930\" width=614 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730580/extras/ac1140800ca7c74fbd09a0dba1717bdd.webm?t=1693311930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730580/extras/ac1140800ca7c74fbd09a0dba1717bdd.mp4?t=1693311930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>搜刮、制作或升级，你可以使用多种手段来装备自己、迎接未来的战斗。还有注意头顶！瑞典军方可是会空投稀有的枪支和护甲哦。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>分数制评分</strong></h2>这不是烂大街的大逃杀游戏，你不必争做活到最后的那个人。每个玩家的目标都是抵达安全之处，但如何抵达就要靠你自己决定了。无论是一路开枪杀出一条血路，还是做个稳扎稳打的工匠，你的所作所为全都会计入总分。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>鸟瞰视角</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730580/extras/e1b167c84d816035be4e2a4497de42ec.poster.avif?t=1693311930\" width=614 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730580/extras/e1b167c84d816035be4e2a4497de42ec.webm?t=1693311930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730580/extras/e1b167c84d816035be4e2a4497de42ec.mp4?t=1693311930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>死亡不是旅程的终点。重生成鸽子回到游戏，成为队伍的终极侦察员吧。",
